Individual




Jarrod B. Pontius



Mr. Jarrod B. Pontius is Secretary & Chief Administrative Officer at Convergys Corp., a Member at Cincinnati Bar Association, a Member at Ohio State Bar Association, and a Member at Association of Corporate Counsel.
Mr. Pontius was previously employed as Secretary, Chief Legal Officer & Vice President by Kendle International, Inc. and Senior Counsel by Kendle International, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Indiana University and a graduate degree from Case Western Reserve University.



