Jarrod Pontius works as General Counsel and Chief Administrative Officer at Convergys Corporation. Mr. Pontius served as Deputy General Counsel of Convergys Corporation. He served as the Chief Legal Officer of Kendle International Inc. since June 2009 and also served as its Vice President and Secretary. Mr. Pontius has more than a decade of experience in both the legal and corporate legal environments. He rejoins Kendle, from General Cable Corporation, where he served as Assistant General Counsel since 2007. Mr. Pontius served as Corporate Counsel and Senior Corporate Counsel for Kendle from 2002 to 2007. Mr. Pontius is a member of both the Cincinnati and Ohio Bar Associations and the Association of Corporate Counsel.



